    "title": "Redirecionando",
    "descriptionContent": "Aprenda como redirecionar páginas que foram movidas e como usar redirecionamento para gerenciar versionamento",
    "shortDescriptionContent": "",
    "showInTrack": true,
    "iconBanner": null,
    "chapters": [
      {
        "id": 15073,
        "title": "Capítulo #1",
        "type": "practiceLevel1",
        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4",
            "id": 132905,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Um redirecionamento é quando um servidor web informa ao seu navegador para ir a uma página diferente.</p><p>Redirecionamentos são essenciais. Eles guiam os usuários para o conteúdo correto quando as páginas são movidas, renomeadas ou com base em condições específicas.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3",
            "id": 132878,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Em vez de retornar uma resposta através do objeto de resposta, chamamos <code>redirect</code> nele.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect();\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"47\" endIndex=\"48\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"56\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>res</code> seguido de <code>.</code> e finalmente <code>redirect</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy",
            "id": 132906,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Nós fornecemos uma nova rota para a qual a solicitação deve ser redirecionada.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"47\" endIndex=\"48\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"56\" /><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"69\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>res</code> seguido de <code>.</code> e depois <code>redirect</code>, <code>\"/new-route\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132908,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Nós respondemos com uma nova rota e, como sempre, um código de status.</p><p>O código de status <code>302 Found</code> indica que o recurso solicitado foi temporariamente movido para a URL fornecida na resposta.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"302\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"60\" /><option startIndex=\"60\" endIndex=\"61\" /><option startIndex=\"62\" endIndex=\"74\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>302</code> seguido de <code>,</code> e finalmente <code>\"/new-route\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy  Copy",
            "id": 132909,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Não precisamos definir explicitamente <code>302 Found</code> pois ele é definido implicitamente se usarmos <code>redirect</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"69\" /><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"47\" endIndex=\"48\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"56\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>res</code> seguido de <code>.</code> e depois <code>redirect</code>, <code>\"/new-route\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132907,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Quando o cliente recebe <code>302 Found</code> junto com uma nova URL, normalmente, ele fará o redirecionamento chamando o endpoint fornecido.</p><p>Aqui, o cliente será redirecionado de <code>\"/old-route\"</code> para <code>\"/new-route\"</code>, recebendo um status <code>200 OK</code> e uma mensagem.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.status(\" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\").send(\" /><text value=\"&quot;You found me!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"20\" /><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"97\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>\"/old-route\"</code> seguido de <code>\"/new-route\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4",
            "id": 132879,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Por outro lado, um redirecionamento permanente <code>301 Moved Permanently</code> sinaliza uma mudança permanente na localização do recurso.</p><p>Vamos mudar nosso redirecionamento temporário anterior para um permanente.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"301\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"60\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"302\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>301</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #5",
            "id": 132880,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Express também permite roteamento baseado em declarações condicionais. Publicar uma nova versão é fácil com redirecionamentos.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/:version&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (req.params.version == \" /><text value=\"&quot;1.0&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  res.send(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Version 1.0&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" } \" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/1.0&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"117\" endIndex=\"120\" /><option startIndex=\"120\" endIndex=\"121\" /><option startIndex=\"121\" endIndex=\"129\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>res</code> seguido de <code>.</code> e finalmente <code>redirect</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4 - Copy",
            "id": 132910,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Você pode usar redirecionamentos ao trabalhar com um router também.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"router.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"router.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"301\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"6\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>router</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132912,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Redirecionar de <code>\"/friends\"</code> para <code>\"/homies\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/friends&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"302\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/homies&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/homies&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.status(\" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\").send(\" /><text value=\"&quot;What's up?&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"94\" /><option startIndex=\"60\" endIndex=\"69\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;/friends&quot;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>\"/friends\"</code> seguido de <code>\"/homies\"</code> e finalmente <code>\"/homies\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #15",
            "id": 132917,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Como você define manualmente o código de status para um redirecionamento no Express?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>res.redirect(301, \"/new-route\")</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>res.redirect(\"/new-route\", 301)</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\"><code>res.redirect(301, \"/new-route\")</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132914,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Defina o código de status para um redirecionamento permanente.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"301\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"60\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"302\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>301</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #17",
            "id": 132919,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Crie um redirecionamento temporário de <code>\"/store\"</code> para <code>\"/shop\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/store&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", (req, res) =&gt; {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"302\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/shop&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/shop&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", (req, res) =&gt; {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.status(\" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\").send(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome to the shop!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"16\" /><option startIndex=\"49\" endIndex=\"52\" /><option startIndex=\"54\" endIndex=\"61\" /><option startIndex=\"77\" endIndex=\"84\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;/store&quot;\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"301\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>\"/store\"</code> seguido de <code>302</code> e depois <code>\"/shop\"</code>, <code>\"/shop\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
